# Case Study: AEC Recruiting Project (Mock)

## Context
Tight market for civil engineers and PMs.

## Approach
- PM framework (charter, milestones, comms plan)
- AI-assisted sourcing + candidate summaries
- Weekly HM syncs and dashboard snapshots

## Results (Mock)
- 85 sourced → 12 screened → 4 final → 2 hires in 40 days

## Lessons
AI sped up sourcing; PM cadence kept stakeholders aligned.
